data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This captivating 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence embodies luxury living, conveniently located minutes from MD-210, the National Harbor, and Downtown DC. Step inside to a grand 2-story foyer and gleaming hardwood floors. The expansive family room features a charming wood-burning fireplace, seamlessly connecting to the open kitchen with designer granite countertops and splash, and solid oak cabinets. Entertain in style in the formal living and dining rooms adorned with elegant crown molding. Retreat to the oversized master suite boasting a massive walk-in closet, luxurious oval soaking tub, and separate shower. Enjoy the convenience of a ground-floor office space with custom built-in bookcases. The fully finished basement offers a vast rec room & storage area, an additional 400sf+ dark room area for studio, theatre room or whatever your thing is! Home being sold "As IS" for seller's convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite property yours. Schedule your appointment today & prepare to fall in love with your new home!
